 og sparebankloven § 22 tredje ledd endret forskrift om legitimasjon av innskuddskonti i forretnings- og sparebanker av 21. november 1975.</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/" id="ledd-2">Forskriftens § 1 første ledd skal lyde:</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/" id="ledd-3">Ved opprettelse av konto for personlig innskyter skal banken registrere innskyterens<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="a)" data-name="a)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/punkt/1/" id="ledd-3-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">a)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="ledd-3-punkt-1-ledd-1">navn</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="b)" data-name="b)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/punkt/2/" id="ledd-3-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">b)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="ledd-3-punkt-2-ledd-1">fødselsnummer (11 siffer)</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="c)" data-name="c)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/punkt/3/" id="ledd-3-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">c)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="ledd-3-punkt-3-ledd-1">adresse.</article></article></li></ul></article></main></body></html>